        "name": "Uncontrollable Dance",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "The target is overcome with an all-consuming urge to dance. For the duration of the spell, the target is off-guard and can't use reactions. It also can't use move actions except to dance, using the Stride action to move up to half its Speed.",
